      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay but is it really that simple though? people talk about how huge the mining footprint is for the rare earth metals in wind turbines and how hard it is to recycle the blades, and some say gas is actually \"cleaner\" in terms of land use or being more reliable for the grid. can u explain why those concerns dont change the outcome?",
